      "text": "A 6-year-old child is brought up due to concerns about persistent fever, fatigue, and frequent infections over the past few weeks. There is generalised lymphadenopathy. Laboratory investigations reveal leukocytosis with lymphoblasts on peripheral smear examination. Which of the following stains are used to visualise lymphoblasts?",
